      <svg viewBox={`0 0 ${W} ${H}`} role="img" aria-label="Spread over SOFR on GPU-collateralized facilities, July 2023 to June 2026. The lowest spreads (+2.25) are the IG-contract-wrapped facilities; the highest (+9.62, +13) are unwrapped or non-IG.">
